# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#  Plaza Delft Monitor — Configuration
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#  Copy to .env and fill in your webhook URL:
#     cp .env.example .env

# ── Discord (REQUIRED) ──────────────────────────
# Right-click channel → Edit Channel → Integrations → Webhooks → New Webhook → Copy URL
DISCORD_WEBHOOK_URL=https://discord.com/api/webhooks/YOUR_WEBHOOK_ID/YOUR_WEBHOOK_TOKEN

# ── Polling (optional) ──────────────────────────
# POLL_MIN_SECONDS=480
# POLL_MAX_SECONDS=900

# ── Filter (optional) ──────────────────────────
# TARGET_CITY=delft
